thread.title: Trump "very happy" House Republicans found no collusion with Russia

title: Trump "very happy" House Republicans found no collusion with Russia
text:
Trump "very happy" House Republicans found no collusion with Russia 10:16pm IST - 00:36 
U.S. House Intelligence Committee Republicans said on Monday the panel had finished investigating Russia and the 2016 U.S. election, and found no collusion between President Donald Trump's campaign and Moscow's efforts to influence the vote. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
